Citation.sAbstract: The isobaric VLE data for three binary systems (DHM + pinane, DHM + DHMOH, pinane + DHMOH) and one  ternary system (pinane + DHM + DHMOH) at 6 kPa were measured with a Rose-Williams still. The binary  VLE data were correlated with the Wilson and NRTL models. With the obtained model parameters, the  ternary (pinane + DHM + DHMOH) VLE data was predicted and compared with the experimental data and  the result shows that the parameters also have a good performance in the prediction of the ternary VLE  data.
Citation.sTitle: Isobaric vapor liquid equilibrium (VLE) for pinane, dihydromyrcene (DHM) and  dihydromyrcenol (DHMOH) at 6 kPa
